<item>
  <title>How I became aware of sexism</title>
  <link>https://klau.si/how-i-became-aware-sexism</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;How I became aware of sexism&lt;/span&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is a cross post to the &lt;a href="http://groups.drupal.org/node/419973"&gt;"ah-ha moment regarding sexism in tech" discussion on groups.drupal.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I have never been devalued because of my gender, that's why I was long blind to sexism and feminism. I thought this topic has been solved since 1920 when women were allowed to vote in Austria.&lt;/p&gt;
